### schema:geo ### {#schema-geo}

<div class="example">
    A place with coordinates:

    <pre highlight=json-ld>
        {
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "Place",
          "geo": {
            "@type": "GeoCoordinates",
            "latitude": "40.75",
            "longitude": "-73.98"
          },
        }
    </pre>
</div>
